1) create a new app witjh routing
   ng new http_crud_app
2) inside it create a folder called as server
3) inside server folder create file database.json
    in that file add below json object:-

    {
	 "books": []
    }
  
  and save the file
4) go to command prompt:- and run below command with -g option
	npm install -g json-server
5) go to server folder from command prompt and start 
   json-server using npx command on port  5000 as shown below.

C:\Namrata_SoftwareDev\angular_30july\Angular_Demos
\angular_examples
\http_crud_app
\server> npx json-server --watch -p 5000 database.json

6) open browser and type below url
   http://localhost:5000/books

   will load database.json in browser and display empty array